## Debug Message (0xF4)
The glasses send debug messages when debugging mode is enabled.The message is a null terminated ASCII string. See [Enable/Disable Debug Mode (0x23 0x6C)](#enable/disable-debug-mode-\(0x23-0x6c\))

| Header | Message |
| :---- | :---- |
| `F4` | `Null Terminated ASCII Data.\0` |

## Device Event (0xF5)

