| `F5` | `05` |  | `TouchPad Triple Tap` |
| `F5` | `06` |  | `Worn` |
| `F5` | `07` |  | `Not worn / Not in case` |
| `F5` | `08` |  | `In Case / Lid open` |
| `F5` | `09` | `00 / 01` | `Glasses side charging` |
| `F5` | `0A` | `00 ~ 64` | `Glasses side battery level` |
