## Set Head Up Action (0x08)

Sets what happens when the user lifts their head up. Send to **Both** sides. [Response is generic](#generic-command-response)  
If the Local / Global is set to 03, the command can be sent to just the left and left will forward to the right? If set to 04, the command sends to both?

| Header | Packet size | Pad | Seq | Local / Global | Action |
| :---- | :---- | :---- | :---- | :---- | :---- |
| `08` | `06` | `00` | `00-FF` | `03 / 04` | `00 / 02` |

### Modes

| Action ID | Action |
| :---- | :---- |
| `00` | `Show the Dashboard` |
| `01` | `??` |
| `02` | `Do Nothing` |

