## Erase DFU (0x17)

After a successful Firmware Update, resources will still be allocated to the DFU firmware image. This command erases the image. **Do NOT send this command unless you REALLY know what you are doing**. Send to Both sides. [Response is generic](#generic-command-response).

| Command |
| :---- |
| `17` |

